Lenny Henry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lenny_Henry 0 Sir Lenworth George Henry (born 29 August 1958) is an English stand-up comedian, actor, singer, writer, and television presenter, known for co-founding the charity Comic Relief, and presenting various television programmes, including the comedy Chef! and The Magicians for BBC One. He is currently the Chancellor of Birmingham City University.
